        Project Pharos is a new mobile fintech solution being developed by State Street Global Exchange, the data & analytics division of State Street Corporation, is developing a new mobile Fintech solution geared for Risk Management professionals. This solution will use a combination of machine learning algorithms and human expertise to identify and curate meaningful connections between news and user portfolios, and then provide a customized measure of impact and relevance based on those portfolios.
